ralrift.org/2014/03/04/steep-steep-ejuice/" rel="bookmark"  class="tptn_link"><span class="tptn_title">To Steep Or Not To Steep An eJuice</span></a></span></li><li><span class="tptn_after_thumb"><a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2013/11/19/switching-to-ecigs-vaping-the-cost-of-vaping/" rel="bookmark"  class="tptn_link"><span class="tptn_title">Switching to eCigs / Vaping: The Cost of Vaping</span></a></span></li><li><span class="tptn_after_thumb"><a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2013/12/03/ecigs-vaping-a-few-words-about-batteries/" rel="bookmark"  class="tptn_link"><span class="tptn_title">eCigs &#038; Vaping: A Few Words About Batteries</span></a></span></li><li><span class="tptn_after_thumb"><a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2013/10/12/warning-green-leaf-tobacco-ejuice/" rel="bookmark"  class="tptn_link"><span class="tptn_title">WARNING: Green Leaf Tobacco eJuice</span></a></span></li><li><span class="tptn_after_thumb"><a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2013/09/24/switching-to-ecigs-vaping-cigarette-withdrawl/" rel="bookmark"  class="tptn_link"><span class="tptn_title">Switching to eCigs / Vaping: Cigarette Withdrawl</span></a></span></li><li><span class="tptn_after_thumb"><a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2013/09/11/the-ecig-vaping-vs-analog-tobacco-cigarettes-experiment/" rel="bookmark"  class="tptn_link"><span class="tptn_title">The eCig (Vaping) vs Analog (Tobacco) Cigarettes Experiment</span></a></span></li></ul></div></aside>			</div>
